      "*A lot of grocery stores have Asian ingredient aisles now.",
      "You should be able to find chili-bean paste, a mixture of preserved chilies mixed with mashed soybeans, there or at any Asian market. (Do not confuse with black bean paste or chili-garlic paste.)",
